data.value:
AAM strategy: At start choose doctor 2. This will double the value of the hang-on score. Very important.
After plunge shoot blue H arrow to the left. When ball returns shoot O arrow until you get sonic boom.
Complete W-H-O arrows for 120M points. Usually players continue to shoow O for next sonic boom. However i like
to let the ball come down to bottom left flipper and shooting W-H-O over and over. Since we are now at
4x playfield each letter scores massive points and don't forget the Hang-On score on top of it!
